#: ./docs/8.x/blade.md:354
#: ./docs/9.x/blade.md:413
#: ./docs/10.x/blade.md:424
#: ./docs/11.x/blade.md:425
#: ./docs/master/blade.md:424
msgctxt "P"
msgid "The `$loop` variable also contains a variety of other useful properties:"
